{"tid":319320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係比自己呃左","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T17:00:03.000Z","uid":36402,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67ac2a6f3ea388abe5a708ca737fc6a3a57799ca","tid":319320,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我對我感覺既發現總係會慢半拍<br />\n我講既當然唔係熱凍痛依種感覺啦，而係對一個人既感情投放同定位，無分友情定愛情，永遠我都會無視或者捉錯自己既感覺。<br />\n就好似今日我感受到我愛你，但回頭發現依種其實唔係愛既感覺。但既然唔係愛，點解我一開始會認為依種感覺係愛，定係我特別鍾意呃自己？"},{"pid":"53a66d2dc8cb684cb1bcc6cc09de4bad6848c452","tid":319320,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"842b7676e84ad97999fe258c94cf10cae7646ce3","tid":319320,"uid":61171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:36:02.000Z","msg":"唔夠了解自己"},{"pid":"5654ad9922b71f0bf73fe496710820e0ded26ee7","tid":319320,"uid":127216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"問世間甚麼叫做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fead062a96f5300c20405dfaf2ccb63b523839ad","tid":319320,"uid":36402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠了解自己</blockquote><br />\n就連自己都唔了解自己係咪可悲？<br />\n定係我唔想去了解一個咁既自己？"},{"pid":"706ccfcaad58e54e944b0156a52b156fa1c3eab1","tid":319320,"uid":61171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔夠了解自己</blockquote><br />\n就連自己都唔了解自己係咪可悲？<br />\n定係我唔想去了解一個咁既自己？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係for both<br />\n<br />\n成長就係了解自己嘅一個過程<br />\n就算唔想，遲早都會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52a452d71ff0c17e3498d89f7d3447184448ea8","tid":319320,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"我成日都問自己咩先叫愛<br />\n好驚以為愛 其實只係佔有或唔甘心<br />\n由拍拖直到分手都未諗到答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/